Pre-Game Insights: Iqraam Rayners is expected to start for Bafana Bafana against Algeria and aims to score one or two goals to impress.
Coach Hugo Broos has highlighted the importance of strikers stepping up to international level, with Rayners auditioning for a place in the World Cup qualifiers.
Rayners has been instrumental for Stellenbosch FC in the 2023-2024 season, scoring crucial goals.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match is set to be played at Stade Nelson Mandela with a capacity of 40,000, indicating high interest and support.
